<h2 id="unix">Unix</h2>

<blockquote>
  <p>Unix is a <strong>family</strong> of multitasking, multiuser computer OS.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>Derive from the original <strong>AT&amp;T Unix</strong>, Developed in the 1970s at <strong>Bell Labs</strong> (è´å°”å®éªŒå®¤), initially intended for use inside the <strong>Bell System</strong>.</p>

