  <li>PROM (Programmable read-only memory)</li>
  <li>EPROM (Erasable programmable read-only memory)</li>
  <li>EEPROM (Electrically erasable programmable read-only memory)
    <ul>
      <li>Flash memory (é—ªå­˜)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

